{"tid":2011301,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中共：紅色經濟圈復播NBA無期 重申香港主權絕不退讓","createTime":"2020-05-11T01:44:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T16:03:11.000Z","uid":21470,"like":32,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"7ba4a140b070bef7303df66f07f0779d407460c0","tid":2011301,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T01:44:09.000Z","msg":"央視否認復播NBA賽事強調主權問題不會含糊<br />\n11.05.2020 08:52<br />\n<br />\n內地中央電視台引述體育頻道負責人，否認恢復轉播美國NBA賽事，指目前與NBA方面沒有任何接觸和交往，重申對中國主權問題態度嚴肅、鮮明和一貫，不會有任何含糊和回旋的餘地，NBA高層應該清楚有關立場。<br />\n<br />\nNBA火箭隊總經理莫雷去年十月發表支持香港反修例示威的言論，引起北京不滿；中央電視台決定暫停轉播NBA賽事，多間內地企業亦封殺NBA，或暫停贊助。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1286644&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1286644%26csid%3D261_341&d=jhMTXyFjUfd7nN31cC%2BnyV8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=4c7e4acb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1286644&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"317ea5e81f8c268c822d9d0f8ef5d619bc41cb20","tid":2011301,"uid":256094,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T01:45:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />陰公囉大陸仔"},{"pid":"86cadb1d8c27054557ea947d7f91aaba2eeb7bb2","tid":2011301,"uid":105976,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T01:47:13.000Z","msg":"加速全世界去中共化  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a706087dbb827c34f4274370caa2d00b3be1e2c6","tid":2011301,"uid"